# One "HOST_PATH:CONTAINER_PATH[:ro|rw]" mount per line.
# Copy to .mounts (or the path set by HOST_MOUNTS_FILE in .env) and edit.
# Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
# Mode defaults to rw if omitted. Prefer ':ro' unless write access is
# actually needed -- make up warns on every writable mount.

# /Users/you/Desktop:/home/desktop/Desktop:rw
# /Users/you/Downloads:/home/desktop/Downloads:ro
